metadata.description:
***Wish You Pepe Here*** is the ninth studio album by the Memeglish rock band Pepe Floyd, released on 12 September 1975 through Meme Records and Kek Records, their first release for the latter. Based on material Pepe Floyd composed while performing in Europe, Wish You Pepe Here was recorded over numerous sessions throughout 1975 at Pepe Road Studios in Memedon.

Year: 2022
